trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection> class allows you to programmatically access a collection of <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection> 클래스의 컬렉션을 프로그래밍 방식으로 액세스할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The collection can be accessed with either the key or the index.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 키나 인덱스를 액세스할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> class.
A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the virtual directory path.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
<paramref name="mapping" /> is <see langword="null" />.
<paramref name="virtualDirectory" /> already exists in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> is read-only.
Returns a string array that contains all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 인스턴스의 모든 키를 포함하는 문자열 배열을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: A string array that contains all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 인스턴스의 모든 키를 포함하는 문자열 배열입니다.

trans-unit.source: Clears all <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> objects from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
A one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>배열</c>에서 복사를 시작할 인덱스입니다. 이 인덱스는 0부터 시작합니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> collection to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 전체 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 컬렉션을 호환되는 1차원 <see cref="T:System.Array" />에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.

The <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> property of <paramref name="array" /> is less than the value of <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> plus <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" />의 <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> 속성이 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" />에 <paramref name="index" />를 더한 값보다 작은 경우

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element.

An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 내의 특정 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 개체를 지정하는 정수 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 인덱스에 있는 지정된 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 컬렉션 요소를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> element at the specified index.
A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element based on the specified virtual-directory name.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 가상 디렉터리 이름을 기반으로 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 컬렉션 요소를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> element based on the specified virtual-directory name.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 가상 디렉터리 이름을 기반으로 한 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 내의 특정 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 개체를 지정하는 정수 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the key of the entry at the specified index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 인스턴스의 지정한 인덱스에서 엔트리의 키를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.

An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 내의 특정 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 개체를 지정하는 정수 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object at the specified index location.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 인덱스 위치의 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 개체를 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object based on the specified virtual directory name.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 가상 디렉터리 이름을 기반으로 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 개체를 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
A string that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
Removes a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.

An integer value that specifies a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> 내의 특정 <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> 개체를 지정하는 정수 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Removes a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object at the specified index from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
